caller_intent: The caller (Jason) had previously attempted to contact an agent but reached voicemail and was now on a recall call.
resolution_steps: System message played requesting caller to think about recent contact information changes.
System promoted online policy management portal (myallianceinsurance.com) and text support (336-786-1133).
summary: A recall call was placed to Jason after a previous voicemail attempt. The system message provided hold instructions and promoted digital self-service options while the agent was unavailable.
